# Files excluded from the published pub.dev tarball (gitignore syntax).
#
# pub.dev publishes everything git-tracked unless listed here. The directories
# below are repo-internal — dev tooling, planning docs, bug reports, the test
# suite, and coverage artifacts. None are consumed by users of the library, and
# they bloated the package (plans/ alone is 130 files). Excluding them shrinks
# the download and keeps the pub.dev "files" view focused on the API surface.
#
# Deliberately KEPT in the package: lib/, example/ (pub.dev renders it),
# assets/ (small), and README/CHANGELOG/LICENSE/pubspec (required or useful).

/test/
/plans/
/tool/
/bugs/
/reports/
/scripts/
/coverage/
